A container, we add events to it and every event added to it produces states. A class that begins with a state and it\'92s output is always a state. For Example; Logged-In, Logged-Out, Error Screen.\
\
For Example: You give input Login with this username and password, Register with this username and password. These are events we give to Bloc. Then it produces output states on those events.\
